      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Simulated hemolysis index and pressure rise compared against five experimental datasets from the FDA interlaboratory study. Normalized root mean square error of 12% for hemolysis index is within accepted tolerance for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
