      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is directly the clinical quantity of interest for CPB device safety assessment. The QoI is mechanistically linked to red blood cell damage through validated power-law stress exposure models, exceeding MRL 2 relevance requirements."
